{"type": "assistant", "message": {"id": "msg_1784096963255", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "我现在已经获取了全文并确立了全面的研究事实锚点。以下是截止研究阶段的关键事实：\n\n**已确立的事实锚点：**\n- 论文全文已从 arXiv HTML (2607.12569v1) 获取 — 3个策略：full retraining、BN-only domain adaptation、domain translation (21K params)\n- 主要 baseline：Salvi et al. (ICASSP 2025) \"Freeze and Learn\" [23] — LCNN with selective freezing\n- 先前持续学习 (CL) 工作用于 audio deepfake：Zhang et al. (AAAI 2024) self-adaptive CL [29]，Ma et al. (Interspeech 2021) KD+similarity [14]，Dong et al. (TENCON 2024) [4]\n- Concurrent/newer: arXiv 2511.19974 (UAP-based continual ADD)，arXiv 2505.24486 (rehearsal-based CL)\n- Adapter approaches 已在 speech forensics 中存在：Wu et al. (Interspeech 2024) 用于反欺骗的 adapter learning，arXiv 2502.10838 (meta-learned LoRA)\n- CORAL loss [24] = Sun & Saenko (ECCV 2016)，为成熟的 domain adaptation 技术\n- Prototype Consistency [30] = Zhang et al. (2025)，出自 semantic segmentation，非 audio\n- 4个数据集：ASVspoof 2019, FoR, ITW, ADD 2022\n- 指标：AUC, EER；源领域 (ASV19) 目标领域 (FoR/ITW/ADD22) trade-off\n- 21K 参数 vs 5556K (CL ALL) — 参数量缩减 264倍\n- Diffusion-based augmentation: 准确率从 0.988 提升至 0.994 (增量为 0.6 个百分点)\n\n我现在已经拥有输出完整审稿所需的所有信息。"}], "model": "GLM-5.2-w4a8", "stop_reason": null, "stop_sequence": null, "usage": {"input_tokens": 0, "output_tokens": 0, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 0}, "context_management": null}, "parent_tool_use_id": null, "session_id": "b0441df7-8fec-4ad0-9933-4da8a89f7629", "uuid": "ecc8a2a7-797c-4c92-98f3-8d5ab7f768a7"}
